	<name>PinApp</name>
	<summary>Create and edit application shortcuts</summary>
    <developer_name translatable="no">Fabrizio Alberio</developer_name>
	<description>
	  <p>With PinApp you can:</p>
	  <ul>
		<li>Easily change an app icon that doesn't fit in with your theme</li>
		<li>Create custom shortcuts to websites</li>
		<li>Hide apps you don't want to see</li>
		<li>Change properties in .desktop files</li>
	  </ul>
	</description>
